#: ../../source/reference/tensor/generated/maxframe.tensor.logaddexp2.rst:2
msgid "maxframe.tensor.logaddexp2"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.logaddexp2.logaddexp2:1 of
msgid "Logarithm of the sum of exponentiations of the inputs in base-2."
msgstr "输入值以2为底的指数和的对数。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.logaddexp2.logaddexp2:3 of
msgid ""
"Calculates ``log2(2**x1 + 2**x2)``. This function is useful in machine "
"learning when the calculated probabilities of events may be so small as "
"to exceed the range of normal floating point numbers.  In such cases the "
"base-2 logarithm of the calculated probability can be used instead. This "
"function allows adding probabilities stored in such a fashion."
msgstr ""
"计算 ``log2(2**x1 + 2**x2)``。在机器学习中，当事件的计算概率小到超出正常"
"浮点数范围时，该函数非常有用。在这种情况下，可以使用计算概率的以2为底的"
"对数。该函数允许以这种方式存储的概率相加。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.logaddexp2.logaddexp2 of
msgid "参数"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.logaddexp2.logaddexp2:9
#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.logaddexp2.logaddexp2:11 of
msgid "Input values."
msgstr "输入值。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.logaddexp2.logaddexp2:13 of
msgid ""
"A location into which the result is stored. If provided, it must have a "
"shape that the inputs broadcast to. If not provided or `None`, a freshly-"
"allocated tensor is returned. A tuple (possible only as a keyword "
"argument) must have length equal to the number of outputs."
msgstr ""
"用于存储结果的位置。如果提供了此参数，则其形状必须能广播到输入值的形状。"
"如果未提供或为 `None`，则返回一个新分配的 tensor。元组（只能作为关键字"
"参数）的长度必须等于输出数量。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.logaddexp2.logaddexp2:18 of
msgid ""
"Values of True indicate to calculate the ufunc at that position, values "
"of False indicate to leave the value in the output alone."
msgstr "为 True 表示在该位置计算 ufunc，为 False 表示保留输出中的值不变。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.logaddexp2.logaddexp2 of
msgid "返回"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.logaddexp2.logaddexp2:23 of
msgid "**result** -- Base-2 logarithm of ``2**x1 + 2**x2``."
msgstr "**result** -- ``2**x1 + 2**x2`` 的以2为底的对数。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.logaddexp2.logaddexp2 of
msgid "返回类型"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.logaddexp2.logaddexp2:28 of
msgid ":py:obj:`logaddexp`"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.logaddexp2.logaddexp2:29 of
msgid "Logarithm of the sum of exponentiations of the inputs."
msgstr "输入值的指数和的对数。"

